@startuml
title Scheduled Discovery - Intent to Intent Matching

actor UserA
actor UserB

participant "API Layer" as API
participant "WalkIntent\n(Aggregate)" as Intent
participant "MatchingService\n(Domain Service)" as Matching
participant "AIService" as AI
participant "MatchProposal\n(Aggregate)" as Proposal
participant "WalkSessionService" as SessionService
participant "WalkSession\n(Aggregate)" as Session

== 1. User A tạo Intent ==

UserA -> API : Create WalkIntent(A)
API -> Intent : create(A)
Intent --> API : IntentCreated

== 2. User B tạo Intent ==

UserB -> API : Create WalkIntent(B)
API -> Intent : create(B)
Intent --> API : IntentCreated

== 3. System detect overlap ==

API -> Matching : findMatches(newIntent)

Matching -> Intent : load open intents
Matching -> Matching : filter by\n- time overlap\n- distance\n- block list

Matching -> AI : rank(intentA, intentB)
AI --> Matching : compatibility score

Matching -> Proposal : create Proposal(A,B)

== 4. Hai bên xác nhận ==

UserA -> API : Accept Proposal
UserB -> API : Accept Proposal

API -> Proposal : confirmBoth()

Proposal -> SessionService : createSession(A,B)

== 5. Tạo WalkSession ==

SessionService -> Session : create(PENDING)
Session --> SessionService : SessionCreated

API --> UserA : Session confirmed
API --> UserB : Session confirmed
@enduml